reviewText: I am a Ralf Little fan and he doesn't appear in Season 7, disappointing, but the show keeps up the slightly raunchy format and stays funny.  I probably won't buy Season 8 and, after watching it once, I probably won't watch it again, but it was as good as it could be without my favorite Ralf.
Original and somewhat crude, but a delightful parody of the North and a group of youngsters living there. Compulsive viewing!
